Body:
Can anybody tell me how to implement collect-view for contiki-2.7/examples/ipv6/simple-udp-rpl/unicast-receiver.c ?

Do I have to refer to

contiki-2.7/examples/ipv6/rpl-collect/collect-common.c & udp.sink.c

or

contiki-2.7/examples/collect collect-view-shell.c

?
I formatted your question so it is more readable. I also made a sentence and remove 'plz help', as if you are asking a question, you are obviously asking for help.
make sure that you already added header file and use sky mote for your simulation. As I know, collection view application is only working on Sky motes.
